reviewText:
Defy Gravity Extended is a great game.
-It doesn't take a lot of time to complete the game (It took me 3.3hrs);
-The price is good (Bought it when it was 0.17$);
-The game is simple yet it's fun and challenging,and sometimes it gets really fustrating but I got used to it;
-The music is good and it matches the theme.
